OL,3,CAsda fined for selling out of date
OL,4,Cfood at two Welsh stores
OL,6,FAsda has been fined #640,000 for
OL,7,Fselling out-of-date food at two of its
OL,8,Fstores in Wales.
OL,10,FTrading Standards officers found 115
OL,11,Fitems, including some that were more
OL,12,Fthan two weeks out of date, at Asda's
OL,13,FLeckwith and Pentwyn stores in Cardiff.
OL,15,FAsda faced four charges relating to
OL,16,Fthe sale of out-of-date food items
OL,17,Fafter food safety officers visited the
OL,18,Fstores on four occasions in 2024.
