OL,3,CAsda fined for selling out of date
OL,4,Cfood at two Welsh stores
OL,6,FA visit to the Leckwith store on
OL,7,FJanuary 17 of that year found 36 out
OL,8,Fof date items, including five tubs of
OL,9,Fspicy mayo dip seven days out of date.
OL,11,FA visit to the Pentwyn store in the
OL,12,FCardiff Gate retail park in March
OL,13,Ffound 25 outdated items, while another
OL,14,Fvisit to the store a month later found
OL,15,F48 items, including some that were 12
OL,16,Fdays out of date.
OL,18,FA second visit to the Leckwith store
OL,19,Fin May found a further six out of date
OL,20,Fitems.
