OL,3,CAsda fined for selling out of date
OL,4,Cfood at two Welsh stores
OL,6,FAsda was given a fine of #640,000 and
OL,7,Fordered to pay #15,115 in costs and a
OL,8,F#2,000 surcharge.
OL,10,FAsda said the prosecution related to
OL,11,Ffood safety breaches that took place
OL,12,Flast year, when a different date code
OL,13,Fchecking process was in use.
OL,15,FAn updated process that had been in
OL,16,Fplace since November involved daily
OL,17,Fmanual checks on all short-life
OL,18,Fproducts and twice-weekly checks on
OL,19,Fevery long-life product.
