OL,3,CAsda fined for selling out of date
OL,4,Cfood at two Welsh stores
OL,6,FAn Asda spokesman said: "We regret
OL,7,Fthat out-of-date food was found on
OL,8,Fsale at two of our Cardiff stores last
OL,9,Fyear and accept that our usual high
OL,10,Fstandards were not upheld.
OL,12,F"Since then, we have introduced a new
OL,13,Fdate code checking process across all
OL,14,Four stores, whereby every short-life
OL,15,Fproduct is checked daily so that
OL,16,Fcustomers can always buy the freshest
OL,17,Fproducts."
